        <abstract> 
<p>Hopes German edition [of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>] has not yet been printed because he has fallen into a most serious blunder [about sexual selection never acting on the young] on pp. 297–9 of vol. 1.</p> 
        </abstract>
